      <title>新西兰财政部对政府债务走势感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/new-zealand-treasury-concerned-by-trajectory-of-government-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级财政部顾问表示，由于人口老龄化加剧了结构性预算赤字，新西兰未来几十年将面临债务上升的问题，这对财政政策来说是一个重大挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/new-zealand-treasury-concerned-by-trajectory-of-government-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:56:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
